最後一場比賽，兩隊都派出於世界大賽上拿下2勝的王牌先發。這也是大聯盟史上第二遭(前一次是1925年世界大賽)。

Gibson因為休息3天狀況回復較佳，他主投9局送出10次三振只被敲出3支安打失2分。Lonborg因為僅僅休息2天便登板，導致他無法發揮100%的壓制力。他雖然順利撐完6局，但是被敲出10支安打狂丟7分。

Gibson不僅連續投出3場完投，他還在5局上敲出陽春砲。6局上Julián Javier的3分砲更是直接宣布紅雀隊的勝利。終場他們以7比2打敗紅襪，拿下球隊4年內的第二座冠軍。

==里程碑==
* 大聯盟於這年開始頒發[[聯盟主席獎盃|聯盟主席獎盃]]給予世界大賽的最終贏家。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://boston.cbslocal.com/top-lists/5-things-you-didnt-know-about-the-world-series-trophy/ |title=5 Things You Didn’t Know About The World Series Trophy |website=[[WBZ-TV|WBZ-TV]] |date=October 31, 2013 |accessdate=October 27, 2019 |archive-date=2020-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219101050/https://boston.cbslocal.com/top-lists/5-things-you-didnt-know-about-the-world-series-trophy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

* [[盧·布羅克|盧·布羅克]]於世界大賽跑出7次盜壘成功，刷新世界大賽最多盜壘的紀錄。其中他在第七戰就演出3次盜壘成功。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/WS_batting.shtml |title=All-time and Single-Season World Series Batting Leaders |website=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]] |accessdate=October 27, 2019 |quote=see Stolen Bases (Season) |archive-date=2018-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180328094058/https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/WS_batting.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

* Ken Brett以19歲又20天之齡成為世界大賽史上最年輕的投手。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2003-nov-20-me-brett20-story.html |title=Ken Brett, 55; Was Youngest Pitcher in World Series History |newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |url-access=limited |date=November 20, 2003 |accessdate=October 27, 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115120510/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2003-nov-20-me-brett20-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>而他合計投了1.1局無安打無失分，他也是紅襪陣中唯一的左投。

* Bob Gibson在世界大賽投出3場完投勝，合計僅被敲出14支安打。追平世界大賽最多完投且被敲出最少安打的紀錄。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://retrosimba.com/2013/10/28/4-series-aces-for-cards-gibson-porter-eckstein-freese/ |title=4 Series aces for Cards: Gibson, Porter, Eckstein, Freese |website=RetroSimba |date=October 28, 2013 |accessdate=October 27, 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115033904/https://retrosimba.com/2013/10/28/4-series-aces-for-cards-gibson-porter-eckstein-freese/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

* 紅雀隊也成為大聯盟第一支在世界大賽上取得3勝1敗領先，卻遲遲等到第七戰才封王的球隊。

